<plot>This documentary treats movie fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Poltergeist, the 1982 horror movie about a family who discovers a terrible secret in their new home. Included are interviews with director Steven Spielberg and other members of the cast and crew, who talk about the experience of making the film, as well as all of the effort that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?574022</url></doc>
